channel.title: VpS Land Wait Time
channel.description: Hello there ladies and gentlemen, I have recently ordered a VPS from "www.vpsland.com" They normally take about 24 hours to get the VPS set up for you, as it has taken for the past 3-4 Times I've bought from them. But this time it has taken alot longer. Since I ordered and Payed for it about 65 hours ago, I just want to know if this is a normal wait time, and, possibly to relate to this situation, give the longest time you've waited for them. Thanks -Skorge
